Package: xapir
Title: An Implementation of X APIs for Social Media Engagement Research
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2024-11-19
Description: Functions connecting to the 'X' APIs <https://developer.x.com/en/docs/x-api>. 
    This package is tailored to students learning about social media and marketing.
